title: [Gyldemar Forest, Crooked Path]
description: The path makes a wide loop around a particularly large oak to the southwest.  A broken branch hangs across the path like a skeletal arm, blocking passage through the forest.

The path makes a wide loop around a particularly large oak to the southwest.  A broken branch hangs across the path like a skeletal arm blocking passage through the forest, a threat to the careless nighttime traveller.
